    <item>
      <title>犯罪及其对经济造成的 400 亿美元损失是南非投票的核心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/crime-corruption-are-key-issues-at-heart-of-south-african-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日益加剧的不安全感和腐败是 5 月 29 日选举前夕的主要问题，预计选举将迫使非洲人国民大会做出权力分享安排。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/crime-corruption-are-key-issues-at-heart-of-south-african-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塑造领导人形象的朝鲜宣传老板去世，享年 94 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/north-korea-propaganda-boss-who-shaped-image-of-leaders-dies-at-94</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金基男是一名宣传策划人，他帮助朝鲜家族王朝建立了个人崇拜，该家族自冷战时期建国以来一直统治朝鲜，他去世，享年 94 岁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/north-korea-propaganda-boss-who-shaped-image-of-leaders-dies-at-94</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 02:53:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佩特罗寻求与哥伦比亚腐败丑闻保持距离</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/petro-seeks-to-distance-himself-from-colombian-graft-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗表示，该国机构存在“结构性腐败”，他试图与最近涉及盟友的贿赂丑闻撇清关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/petro-seeks-to-distance-himself-from-colombian-graft-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 01:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登强化 2024 年焦点，白宫提拔新闻助理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/white-house-promotes-press-aides-as-biden-sharpens-2024-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新闻秘书卡琳·让-皮埃尔的高级副手离职后，白宫正在提拔两名长期新闻助理，作为在乔·拜登总统竞选连任之前加强新闻办公室运营的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/white-house-promotes-press-aides-as-biden-sharpens-2024-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:34:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪正在赢得印度女性的支持，使其在下一届任期内获得多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/women-voters-could-be-key-to-modi-winning-the-india-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度首都新德里郊区举行的一年一度的热门贸易展览会上，萨罗吉尼正忙着与顾客讨价还价纱丽，这是一种传统的印度服装，通常设计华丽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/women-voters-could-be-key-to-modi-winning-the-india-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯托米·丹尼尔斯的亲密证词暴露了特朗普的私生活</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/intimate-details-from-trump-s-affair-with-stormy-daniels-exposed-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，唐纳德·特朗普与一名成人电影明星的亲密时刻在公开法庭上展开，斯托米·丹尼尔斯在备受期待的封口费审判中描述了她与这位前总统的恋情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/intimate-details-from-trump-s-affair-with-stormy-daniels-exposed-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 22:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官无限期推迟文件案件审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/trump-judge-in-documents-case-postpones-trial-indefinitely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普因涉嫌不当处理机密文件而接受的刑事审判被无限期推迟，这对美国司法部在 11 月总统大选前获得陪审团裁决的努力造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/trump-judge-in-documents-case-postpones-trial-indefinitely</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 21:03:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平抵达塞尔维亚加强与欧洲东部地区的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-s-xi-arrives-in-serbia-to-bolster-ties-with-europe-s-east</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在欧洲之行的第二站抵达塞尔维亚，他试图加强北京对这个巴尔干国家的拥抱，而不是与大多数欧洲国家的关系变得更加困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-s-xi-arrives-in-serbia-to-bolster-ties-with-europe-s-east</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 20:05:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥大学在没有逮捕的情况下清理营地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/uchicago-ends-pro-palestinian-campus-encampment-without-arrests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麻省理工学院表示，数十名学生抗议者正在被停学，而芝加哥大学在美国校园持续紧张的情况下关闭了一个亲巴勒斯坦营地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/uchicago-ends-pro-palestinian-campus-encampment-without-arrests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 13:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
